    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "Dashboard Navigation",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 11 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Dashboards\n\n| Dashboard | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| [Service Overview](/d/service-overview) | RED metrics (Rate, Errors, Duration) for all services |\n| [Backend JVM](/d/backend-jvm) | JVM heap, GC, threads, HikariCP for Spring Boot |\n| [Reasoning Service](/d/reasoning-service) | Python runtime, request metrics by endpoint |\n| [Distributed Traces](/d/distributed-traces) | Tempo trace search with service and duration filters |\n| [Log Explorer](/d/log-explorer) | Centralized logs with trace ID correlation |",
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "title": "Alerts (Future)",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 11 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Alerting\n\nAlert rules and notification channels will be configured in a future epic.\n\n**Planned alerts:**\n- Error rate > 5% for any service\n- P95 latency > 2s for any service\n- JVM heap > 80% of max\n- HikariCP pending connections > 0 for extended period\n- Log error rate spike detection\n\n*See: Future Considerations in the OBS-1 epic.*",
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false }
      }
    }
  ],
